Italy drew 1-1 with England in a friendly at the Juventus Stadium on Tuesday night . 
  Graziano Pelle scored for Italy but Andros Townsend equalised for England . 
  Antonio Conte insisted his return to Turin prompted 'fond memories' The Italy manager reportedly received death threats in the days leading up to the friendly . 
  Conte took over as Italy boss in August after Cesare Prandelli resigned . 
 